INSERT INTO `exercises` VALUES (1,'Bench press','Chest & Triceps','A compound exercise that targets the chest, triceps, and shoulders. Can be performed with a barbell, dumbbells, or a machine.','Lie on a flat bench with your feet firmly planted on the ground. Grasp the barbell with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Lift the barbell off the rack and lower it to your chest. Press the barbell back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms.'),(2,'Squat','Legs & Glutes','A compound exercise that targets the legs and glutes. Can be performed with a barbell, dumbbells, or a machine.','Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a barbell on your upper back with an overhand grip. Lower your body as if you were sitting back into a chair, keeping your back straight and your knees behind your toes. Push through your heels to return to the starting position.'),(3,'Deadlift','Back & Legs','A compound exercise that targets the back, legs, and glutes. Can be performed with a barbell, dumbbells, or a kettlebell.','Stand with your feet hip-width apart, holding a barbell in front of your thighs with an overhand grip. Hinge at the hips and bend your knees to lower the barbell to the ground. Keep your back straight and push through your heels to lift the barbell back up to the starting position.'),(4,'Leg press','Legs','An isolation exercise that targets the quadriceps. Can be performed with a machine.','Sit on a leg press machine with your feet shoulder-width apart on the platform. Release the safety catches and press the platform away from your body until your legs are fully extended. Slowly lower the platform back to the starting position.'),(5,'Lat pulldown','Lats','An isolation exercise that targets the lats. Can be performed with a machine.','Sit on a lat pulldown machine with your feet firmly planted on the ground. Grasp the bar with an overhand grip, slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Pull the bar down to your chest, keeping your elbows close to your body. Slowly release the bar back to the starting position.'),(6,'Shoulder press','Shoulders','An isolation exercise that targets the shoulders. Can be performed with a barbell, dumbbells, or a machine.','Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a barbell at shoulder level with an overhand grip. Press the barbell overhead until your arms are fully extended. Slowly lower the barbell back to the starting position.'),(7,'Bicep curl','Biceps','An isolation exercise that targets the biceps. Can be performed with a barbell, dumbbells, or a machine.','Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand with an underhand grip. Curl the dumbbells up to your shoulders, keeping your elbows close to your body. Slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.'),(8,'Tricep extension','Triceps','An isolation exercise that targets the triceps. Can be performed with a barbell, dumbbells, or a machine.','Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand at shoulder level with an overhand grip. Extend your arms overhead, fully extending your elbows. Slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.'),(9,'Leg curl','Legs','An isolation exercise that targets the hamstrings. Can be performed with a machine.','Lie face down on a leg curl machine with your ankles under the pad. Lift the pad by contracting your hamstrings, keeping your hips on the bench. Slowly lower the pad back to the starting position.'),(10,'Leg extension','Legs','An isolation exercise that targets the quadriceps. Can be performed with a machine.','Sit on a leg extension machine with your legs under the pad. Lift the pad by contracting your quadriceps, keeping your feet pointed forward. Slowly lower the pad back to the starting position.'),(11,'Calf raise','Legs','An isolation exercise that targets the calves. Can be performed with a barbell, dumbbells, or a machine.','Stand with your feet hip-width apart, holding a barbell at your sides or using a calf raise machine. Raise your heels by contracting your calves, keeping your toes pointed forward. Slowly lower your heels back to the starting position.'),(12,'Abdominal crunch','Abs','An isolation exercise that targets the abs. Can be performed with a mat or a machine.','Lie on your back with your knees bent and your hands behind your head. Lift your shoulders off the ground by contracting your abs. Slowly lower your shoulders back to the starting position.'),(13,'Push-up','Chest & Triceps','A bodyweight exercise that targets the chest and triceps. Can be modified to increase or decrease difficulty.','Begin in a plank position with your hands slightly wider than shoulder-width apart. Lower your body until your chest touches the ground, then push back up to the starting position. Keep your body straight and your core engaged throughout the movement.'),(14,'Dumbbell curl','Biceps','An isolation exercise that targets the biceps. Can be performed with a dumbbell in each hand.','Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand with an underhand grip. Curl the dumbbells up to your shoulders, keeping your elbows close to your body. Slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.'),(15,'Tricep dips','Triceps','An isolation exercise that targets the triceps. Can be performed with a bench or a pair of parallel bars.','Stand facing away from a bench or parallel bars with your hands grasping the edges. Lower your body until your arms form a 90-degree angle, then push back up to the starting position. Keep your body straight and your core engaged throughout the movement.'),(16,'Cable chest fly','Chest','An isolation exercise that targets the chest. Can be performed with a cable machine.','Stand facing a cable machine with your feet shoulder-width apart, grasping the handles with an overhand grip. Step back to create tension on the cable. Bring the handles together in front of your chest, keeping your arms slightly bent. Slowly release the handles back to the starting position.'),(17,'Lateral raise','Shoulders','An isolation exercise that targets the shoulders. Can be performed with dumbbells or a cable machine.','Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a dumbbell in each hand at your sides. Lift the dumbbells out to your sides until they are shoulder level, keeping your elbows slightly bent. Slowly lower the dumbbells back to the starting position.'),(18,'Abdominal Russian twist','Abs','An isolation exercise that targets the abs. Can be performed with a medicine ball or a dumbbell.','Sit on the ground with your knees bent and your heels touching the ground. Hold a medicine ball or dumbbell at your chest with both hands. Lean back slightly and lift your feet off the ground. Twist your torso to the left, then to the right. Repeat for the desired number of reps.'),(19,'Dumbbell bench press','Chest & Triceps','A compound exercise that targets the chest and triceps. Can be performed with a pair of dumbbells.','Lie on a flat bench with your feet firmly planted on the ground. Hold a dumbbell in each hand with an overhand grip. Lower the dumbbells to your chest, then press them back up to the starting position, fully extending your arms.'),(20,'Barbell squat','Legs & Glutes','A compound exercise that targets the legs and glutes. Can be performed with a barbell.','Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart, holding a barbell on your upper back with an overhand grip. Lower your body as if you were sitting back into a chair, keeping your back straight and your knees behind your toes. Push through your heels to return to the starting position.'),(21,'Seated row','Back & Biceps','A compound exercise that targets the back and biceps. Can be performed with a cable machine or a dumbbell.','Sit on a seated row machine or stand facing a cable machine with your feet shoulder-width apart, grasping the handle with an overhand grip. Pull the handle towards your chest, keeping your elb